{"tid":958174,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[貓]生左粒野","createTime":"2018-12-27T14:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T08:59:09.000Z","uid":79351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46ccc926ca006aa75192240e063757d017d88559","tid":958174,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"今朝見到隻貓排齊手腳扮咩乖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6YmDm3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6YmDm3.png&h=0d4f94fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係發現佢隻手多左粒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wO542d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wO542d.png&h=736aa63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以為污糟野點知點搽都搽唔甩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4heYnw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4heYnw.png&h=18a96d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1YYFAT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1YYFAT.png&h=4ebd96fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摸落去似肉既質地<br />\n但硬硬地<br />\n佢又唔痛唔知咩黎<br />\n雖然我隻貓成日咬到我流哂血<br />\n仲要係我沖涼個陣柯屎<br />\n抽氣扇吸哂d屎味入黎<br />\n仲有無數既仆街野<br />\n但我都想佢健健康康攪攪陣<br />\n有無人知係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽朝會帶佢睇醫生<br />\n但等唔到聽朝好想知佢咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d864c873d64d126d5b103c4d34f41830728e91f","tid":958174,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"生滋貓"},{"pid":"b1a25da0758dbff1d58c212adf439d70aa2c181a","tid":958174,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d864c873d64d126d5b103c4d34f41830728e91f","tid":958174,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T15:03:18.000Z","m